Package member

Class Member

java.lang.Object
member.Member
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Member>
Direct Known Subclasses:
Family
public class Member extends Object implements Comparable<Member>
This class defines all the characteristics of a Member. These include:
  • String First Name
  • String Last Name
  • Date Date of Birth
  • Date Expiration Date
  • Location Gym Location
Author:
Hasnain Ali, Carolette Saguil

    • compareTo

      public int compareTo(Member member)
      Compares two members together by last name then first name.
      Specified by:
      compareTo in interface Comparable<Member>
      Parameters:
      member - Member to be compared.
      Returns:
      0 if the members' names are the same, a value less than 0 if the current instance member's name is lexicographically less than the member argument's name, and a value greater than 0 if the current instance member's name is lexicographically greater than the member argument's name.
